info.description:
Currently Brainiac Is Entirely Python, And Has Two Modules:
1:dict: Dict Is A Python Style Diction Containing English Words As Keys, And
Their Definitions As Their Value. dict Also Contains A Few Functions For Using
This Information

2:Writer:Writer Is Dependent On PIL, It Takes As Input A String And Outputs An
Image File Containing The Given String Written In My Handwriting!

If You Can Help Me Out With The Development Of This Project It Is Hosted At
Google Code
